IndividualHistory.name: IndividualHistory
IndividualHistory.description: Represents the history of changes to values in the fields of a data privacy record, based on the Individual object.

DataType.description: Data type of the field that was changed.

Field.description: The name of the changed field.

IndividualId.description: ID of the data privacy record. Label is Individual ID.

NewValue.description: The updated value of the changed field.

OldValue.description: The previous value of the changed field.
